            <h2 class="legal__h2">2. License</h2>
            <p class="muted">
              The software is distributed under the <strong>MIT License</strong>. Full license text:{' '}
              <a href={licenseUrl} target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">{licenseUrl}</a>
            </p>

            <h2 class="legal__h2">3. Disclaimer & limitation of liability</h2>
            <p class="muted" style="font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: 0.02em;">
              THE SOFTWARE IS PROVIDED “AS IS”, WITHOUT WARRANTY OF ANY KIND, EXPRESS OR IMPLIED.
            </p>
            <p class="muted" style="font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: 0.02em;">
              IN NO EVENT SHALL THE AUTHOR OR COPYRIGHT HOLDERS BE LIABLE FOR ANY CLAIM, DAMAGES OR OTHER LIABILITY.
            </p>

            <h2 class="legal__h2">4. Prohibited use</h2>
            <p class="muted" style="font-weight: 900;">DO NOT USE VPS STUDIO FOR:</p>
            <ul class="muted" style="margin: 0; padding-left: 18px;">
              <li>Safety-critical or mission-critical systems</li>
              <li>Production environments without thorough testing and a recovery plan</li>
              <li>Any illegal activity (unauthorized access, malware distribution, IP infringement)</li>
            </ul>

            <h2 class="legal__h2">5. User requirements</h2>
            <p class="muted">
              You confirm that you are <strong>18+</strong> (or the age of majority in your country).
            </p>
            <p class="muted">Using VPS Studio typically requires:</p>
            <ul class="muted" style="margin: 0; padding-left: 18px;">
              <li>Basic understanding of VPS/server administration</li>
              <li>SSH/Docker basics</li>
              <li>Ability to troubleshoot issues independently</li>
